oai_dc:dc.dc:description: University of Tennessee (U.T.) from K + A tracks over Cumberland Avenue. March 30, 1922. Ordered by the Knoxville Journal. Billboards for Calumet Baking Powder, Poll Parrot shoes, Chesterfield Cigarettes, and Jewett. H.F. Copeland Cash Grocery on side of building. Car at right.
